    {
      "_id": "ZadVFWH9sxEziiup",
      "name": "Engolir",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Teste de Resistência de Força: CD 27, one Large or smaller creature Agarrado by the tarrasque (it can have up to six creatures swallowed at a time). O alvo is swallowed, and a condição Agarrado ends. A swallowed creature has the Cego and Impedido conditions and can't teleport, it has Total Cover against attacks and other effects outside the tarrasque, and it takes 56 (16d6) dano de ácido at the start of each of the tarrasque's turns.\nIf the tarrasque takes 60 de dano or more on a single turn from uma criatura inside it, the tarrasque must succeed on a CD 20 Constituição saving throw at the end of that turn or regurgitate all swallowed creatures, each of which falls in a space within 3 m of the tarrasque and fica com a condição Caído. If the tarrasque dies, any swallowed creature no longer fica com a condição Impedido and can escape from the corpse using 6 m of movement, exiting Caído.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
